items.title: Block deals: Mithun Sacheti buys 1.75% stake in Arihant Foundations and Housing Ltd
items.description: Monet Securities Private Ltd sold 3.48 lakh shares of Arihant Foundations & Housing Ltd in two tranches of 1.74 lakh shares each.

items.title: Market extends gain in second week; rupee marginally lower
items.description: Foreign Institutional Investors (FIIs) extended their selling in week ended November 29 as they sold equities worth Rs 5,026.77 crore, while Domestic Institutional Investors (DII) bought equities worth Rs 6,924.78 crore.

items.title: NSE revises expiry day for index derivatives contracts, effect change from January 1
items.description: The Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE) in a circular issued on November 28 said that the weekly contracts of Sensex will expiry on Tuesday of every week from Friday every week.

items.title: More than 100 smallcaps give double-digit return as broader indices outperform
items.description: The BSE Smallcap index surged 5 percent with Ashapura Minechem, Man Infraconstruction, Jai Corp, Bliss GVS Pharma, Bharat Dynamics, Fedbank Financial Services, Garden Reach Shipbuilders & Engineers, Cochin Shipyard, and Capacite Infraprojects rising between 20-39%.
